description:
This week, the remarkable Bella Thorne (MIDNIGHT SUN, FAMOUS IN LOVE) joins Anna and Sim for an all-new episode of Unqualified! First, Bella introduces us to her puppy, Tampon, and tells us about her crying habits, both on and off camera. Then, Bella talks about her favorite character role and why she loves living in Los Angeles. Next, Anna hosts a round of deal breakers before she and Bella discuss murder methods and recurring dreams. After that, Anna proposes a new reality show based on the infamous Oakwood apartments before calling Sam, whose boyfriend has been flirtatiously texting other girls, and Dylan, who dislikes his long-time BFF’s boyfriend. Enjoy, dear listeners!
